youtube"><iframe title="[#HoloEarth] 引入管理人工智能密特拉！ 《另类城市 v1》[Holo Earth TV]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GRpgE5GoKcw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><h2 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">新区域“另类城市v1” </h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" data-attachment-id="125353" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/holoearth-new-area-alternative-city-v1-opens-on-may-16-2024/holoearth-new-area-alternative-city-v1-opens-on-may-16-2024-2/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/holoearth-new-area-alternative-city-v1-opens-on-may-16-2024.jpg" data-orig-size="1920,1080" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="ホロアース 新エリア「オルタナティブ・シティv1」5月16日にオープン" data-image-description="&lt;p>;ホロアース 新エリア「オルタナティブ・シティv1」5月16日にオープン&lt;/p>;
